  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/">Inghams</a>, one of the UK’s largest ski tour operators and one of the longest established, is a proud nominee for the category of <strong>Best Ski &amp; Winter Sports Tour Operator</strong> in the <a href="https://www.britishtravelawards.com/">British Travel Awards 2018</a>.</p>
<p>The prestigious awards honour the very best companies in Travel, as voted by consumers. Eighty-three categories cover the services used by the public when planning and purchasing their holiday experiences, making the British Travel Awards the largest survey of consumer opinion.</p>
<p>Consumer voting opens on <strong>2<sup>nd</sup> July 2018</strong> and will run until <strong>30<sup>th</sup> September 2018</strong>. The Gala Awards Ceremony - when the winners of each category are announced - will take place on 28<sup>th</sup> November 2018.</p>
<p>Inghams is one of the UK’s most experienced specialist tour operators, founded in 1934 by Walter Ingham, who loved the mountains and loved sharing his passion with others. Today, the brand continues to deliver excellent, award-winning holidays that offer value for money. With the recent launch of its Ski 18/19 main edition brochure, Inghams has again extended its winter programme in <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-resorts">Europe</a> and <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-resorts/canada">Canada</a>, offering plenty of choice and flexibility for the coming winter season, ensuring guests can find their perfect winter holiday.</p>]]></bodyText>
